    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Downtown Commercial Core</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood surrounds the Stephen Avenue Walk and is Downtown Calgaryâ€™s most flourishing commercial hotspot.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">With an array of pubs, restaurants, art galleries, nightclubs, cinemas and shopping malls
                located within the neighborhood, there will never be a dull moment in the life of its residents.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Renowned as being the densest downtown neighborhood among all similar sized cities in
                North America, the community in Downtown Commercial Core boasts of being home to around eight of the ten
                tallest skyscrapers in the whole of Western Canada. </p>
